  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Great Lakes Programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This programme has multiple strands:  Strand 1: A project to deliver sustained and effective dialogue between security forces and local communities. Strand 2: A series of projects to support regional peacebuilding efforts by securing institutional change on human rights in Burundi. Strand 3: Monitoring and responding to conflict risks and supporting the conditions needed to allow for peaceful and fair elections in Burundi by 2020. This is an ODA and non-ODA integrated programme. The spend reported against this programme is the ODA element alone.</narrative>
  </description>
